any people wanting to try yoga as part of their daily routine this kind of modification of the classical Sun Salutations is beginning to be appreciated by all age groups with different body structures.";i:49;s:170:"With Sanksrit names like Utkatasana and Trikonasana yoga poses may sound a lot more like spells youd learn at Hogwarts than shapes you can actually get your body to make.";i:50;s:88:"An asana is a posture whether for traditional hatha yoga or for modern yoga as exercise.";i:51;s:201:"37 new yoga poses name in hindi pose idea at home image result for yoga cool posters retro chart yoga poses names in hindi new simple asanas yoga asanas with pictures and names in hindi archives poses.";i:52;s:121:"Each month well include five chair yoga poses inspired by a particular theme along with a recommended yoga book for kids.";i:53;s:72:"This months theme is animals These five yoga animal poses could be done.";i:54;s:42:"During a transition time in the classroom.";i:55;s:53:"During a subject change in your homeschool classroom.";i:56;s:33:"At home when youre stuck indoors.";i:57;s:76:"This version of Chair pose challenges your balance and stretches the glutes.";i:58;s:86:"It gives you a similar stretch in the outsides of your hips to Pigeon and Dead Pigeon.";i:59;s:80:"This variation challenges your balance and builds strength in the feet and legs.";i:60;s:22:"Chair To Forward Bend.";i:61;s:25:"Strengthening Yoga Poses.";i:62;s:24:"Forward Bend Yoga Poses.";i:63;s:22:"So what is chair yoga.";i:64;s:88:"Chair yoga consists of specific poses that require the body to be in a sitting position.";i:65;s:30:"Its also known as seated yoga.";i:66;s:30:"Yoga is a low-impact exercise.";i:67;s:116:"It improves flexibility blood circulation and muscle function without putting a lot of stress on the bones or heart.";i:68;s:51:"Gentle chair yoga is an even lower-impact exercise.";i:69;s:79:"Chair yoga is especially beneficial for people who cant do complex yoga asanas.";i:70;s:99:"If you face difficulty while performing standing and sitting yoga poses chair yoga is just for you.";i:71;s:47:"All you need is a chair and you are good to go.";i:72;s:108:"The below given asanas will not only stretch your bodys muscles but also help in enhancing your flexibility.";i:73;s:106:"Chair Yoga Sequence for Seniors Many senior citizens practice yoga regularly for a healthy and happy life.";i:74;s:90:"Some may not be medically fit to stand or fatigue out if they stand for elongated periods.";i:75;s:126:"As a yoga teacher you may use the senior yoga sequences for the elderly who want to practice but are unable to stand for long.";}}